表格维修表的代码预览

drop index 车辆品牌与维修单_FK on instation;

drop index 维修状态_FK on instation;

drop index 技工与维修表_FK on instation;

drop index instation_PK on instation;

drop table if exists instation;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: instation */
/*==============================================================*/
create table instation
(
insid int not null,
wxstateid int,
artisanid varchar(50),
ctsid int,
instation varchar(20),
jsyuan varchar(20),
joininstimes date,
predictcompletetime date,
predicttime date,
budgetmoney float(10),
insevent varchar(100),
iszn bool,
ifjs bool,
primary key (insid)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: instation_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index instation_PK on instation
(
insid
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: 技工与维修表_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index 技工与维修表_FK on instation
(
artisanid
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: 维修状态_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index 维修状态_FK on instation
(
wxstateid
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: 车辆品牌与维修单_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index 车辆品牌与维修单_FK on instation
(
ctsid
);

alter table instation add constraint FK_技工与维修表 foreign key (artisanid)
references artisan (artisanid) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table instation add constraint FK_维修状态 foreign key (wxstateid)
references wxstate (wxstateid) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table instation add constraint FK_车辆品牌与维修单 foreign key (ctsid)
references cartypes (ctsid) on delete restrict on update restrict;
